### Component 5: universal.js — The Safety Net

#### [NEW] [universal.js](file:///c:/Projects/Textbook%20agent/backend/src/textbook_agent/infrastructure/renderer/assets/universal.js)

Runs first on every generated page, unconditionally. Implements:
1. **Nav anchor smooth scroll** — intercepts clicks on `a[href^="#"]`
2. **Reading progress bar** — creates a fixed bar at document top, updates on scroll
3. **Hint toggle baseline** — finds `.hint` elements without `data-behaviour`, wraps with toggle
4. **Diagram zoom detection** — auto-adds zoom trigger to `<svg>` elements where text < 10px
5. **Table overflow scroll** — wraps any `<table>` wider than its container in a scroll wrapper
6. **Keyboard navigation** — arrow keys move focus between `[data-section-index]` sections
7. **External link safety** — adds `target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"` to external links

~150–200 lines of vanilla JS. No dependencies. Uses `DOMContentLoaded` event.

#### [NEW] [universal.css](file:///c:/Projects/Textbook%20agent/backend/src/textbook_agent/infrastructure/renderer/assets/universal.css)

Styles for universal features: progress bar, zoom triggers, scroll wrappers, print overrides for all hidden content.

